snippet.title: Elon Musk Courted Amber Heard for a Friendship Years Ago, According to Email Exchanges
snippet.description:
Elon Musk Courted Amber Heard for a Friendship Years Ago, According to Email Exchanges
Amber Heard has been making headlines following her divorce from Johnny Depp as she's been spotted out and about several times with Tesla founder Elon Musk. But while the pairing may seem rather random, the two have actually known each other for quite some time.
